PART 3: THE (5,6)-RECURRENCE x(n) = 5x(n-1) - 6x(n-2)
======================================================================

  This recurrence has characteristic polynomial z²-5z+6 = (z-2)(z-3).
  General solution: x(n) = A·2^n + B·3^n

  Different initial conditions give different sequences:

             name   x(0)   x(1)  x(2..8)
  ---------------  -----  -----  ------------------------------
              2^n      1      2  4, 8, 16, 32, 64, 128, 256
              3^n      1      3  9, 27, 81, 243, 729, 2187, 6561
        3^n - 2^n      0      1  5, 19, 65, 211, 665, 2059, 6305
        3^n + 2^n      2      7  23, 73, 227, 697, 2123, 6433, 19427
      2·3^n - 2^n      1      4  14, 46, 146, 454, 1394, 4246, 12866
       H=1 (init)      1      5  19, 65, 211, 665, 2059, 6305, 19171
       H=3 (init)      3      9  27, 81, 243, 729, 2187, 6561, 19683

======================================================================
PART 4: I(x) AT x = 5, 6, 7, 8 — FORMULAS FROM OCF
======================================================================

  The OCF gives I(Ω, x) = Σ_S x^|S| where S ranges over independent sets.
  With x=2: H = I(2) = 1 + 2α₁ + 4α₂ + 8α₃ + ...

  For general x:
    I(x) = 1 + x·α₁ + x²·α₂ + x³·α₃ + ...

  where α_k = number of independent sets of size k in CG(T).

  So the FULL information is encoded in the sequence (α₁, α₂, α₃, ...).

  At n=5 (where α₂ is the max level):
    I(x) = 1 + x·α₁ + x²·α₂

  Relations:
    I(2) = H = 1 + 2α₁ + 4α₂
    I(3) = 1 + 3α₁ + 9α₂
    I(5) = 1 + 5α₁ + 25α₂
    I(6) = 1 + 6α₁ + 36α₂
    I(7) = 1 + 7α₁ + 49α₂
    I(8) = 1 + 8α₁ + 64α₂

  FORMULAS (using α₂ = (H - 1 - 2α₁)/4):

    I(3) = (9H + (-6)α₁ + (-5)) / 4
         = (9H -6·α₁ -5) / 4

    I(5) = (25H + (-30)α₁ + (-21)) / 4
         = (25H -30·α₁ -21) / 4

    I(6) = (36H + (-48)α₁ + (-32)) / 4
         = (36H -48·α₁ -32) / 4
         = (9H -12·α₁ -8) / 1

    I(7) = (49H + (-70)α₁ + (-45)) / 4
         = (49H -70·α₁ -45) / 4

    I(8) = (64H + (-96)α₁ + (-60)) / 4
         = (64H -96·α₁ -60) / 4
         = (16H -24·α₁ -15) / 1

    I(11) = (121H + (-198)α₁ + (-117)) / 4
         = (121H -198·α₁ -117) / 4

